biography.bio: Waltraut Haas was born on June 9, 1927 in Vienna, Austria as Waltraute Haas. She is an actress, known for Mon ami le clown (1955), Premier avril an 2000 (1952) and The White Horse Inn (1960). She was previously married to Erwin Strahl.
biography.name: Waltraut Haas

biography.bio: Herta Talmar is an actress, known for Der Vetter aus Dingsda (1960), The Empress (1962) and Gasparone (1962).
biography.name: Herta Talmar

biography.bio: Kurt Großkurth was born on May 11, 1909 in Langenselbold, Hesse, Germany. He was an actor, known for Ludwig - Le crépuscule des Dieux (1973), August (1961) and Landarzt Dr. Brock (1967). He was married to Martel Großkurth. He died on May 29, 1975 in Bad Aibling, Bavaria, Germany.
biography.name: Kurt Großkurth

biography.bio: Gunnar Möller was born on July 1, 1928 in Berlin, Germany as Gunnar Thor Karl Möller. He is an actor, known for Piroschka (1955), L'ombre de l'étoile rouge (1960) and The Odessa File (1974). He has been married to Christiane Hammacher since 2003. He was previously married to Brigitte Rau.
biography.name: Gunnar Möller

biography.bio: Philipp Gehly is an actor, known for Gasparone (1962).
biography.name: Philipp Gehly

biography.bio: Born in Vienna, Austria, following Matura at Wiener Oberrealschule studied for 1 year music (violin) before moving on to absolve the Max-Reinhardt-Seminar (1945/46) His first parts were on "Theater an der Josefstadt, Vienna". He is now married the third time and is father of 7 children.
biography.name: Gerhard Riedmann

biography.bio: Heinz-Maria Lins is an actor, known for Der fidele Bauer (1962), Das Märchen vom unzufriedenen Tannenbäumchen - Ein weihnachtliches Spiel (1968) and Gasparone (1962).
biography.name: Heinz-Maria Lins

biography.bio: Edd Stavjanik was born on October 12, 1927 in Vienna, Austria. He was an actor, known for Karriere (1963), Zwischenfall in Antiochia (1967) and Les héritiers (1983). He died on October 28, 2008 in Vienna.
biography.name: Edd Stavjanik

biography.bio: Willy Hofmann is an actor, known for Wie es euch gefällt - Ein großer bunter Nachmittag (1957), Gasparone (1962) and Der Bettelstudent (1961).
biography.name: Willy Hofmann

biography.bio: Topsy Küppers was born on August 17, 1931 in Aachen, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. She is an actress, known for Saison in Oberbayern (1956), Un maître coq ou un diner intime (1969) and Uns gefällt die Welt (1956). She was previously married to Georg Kreisler.
biography.name: Topsy Küppers

biography.bio: Rita Bartos is an actress, known for The Empress (1962), Der fidele Bauer (1962) and Gasparone (1962).
biography.name: Rita Bartos

biography.bio: Irene Mann was born on April 12, 1929 in Königsberg, East-Prussia, Germany. She is known for her work on Die Stadt (1966), Ferien vom Ich (1963) and Un môme sur les bras (1958). She was married to Berno von Cramm. She died on September 19, 1996 in Pfaffenhofen an der Ilm, Bavaria, Germany.
biography.name: Irene Mann

biography.bio: Iris Velleuer is an actress, known for Gasparone (1962).
biography.name: Iris Velleuer

biography.bio: Herbert Prikopa was born on November 30, 1935 in Vienna, Austria. He was an actor and writer, known for Bombenwalzer (1968), The Tailor from Ulm (1978) and Der Hochzeitsgast (1962). He died on December 8, 2015 in Vienna.
biography.name: Herbert Prikopa

biography.bio: Alexander Franquet is an actor, known for Gasparone (1962).
biography.name: Alexander Franquet
